<noinclude>
==Documentation==
Closes the company page layout and renders the sidebar.

Place this at the end of company page content, after all wiki text.

===Usage===
<pre>
{{Company
| Name = Example Company
| Deck = Short description...
| City = San Francisco
| Country = USA
...
}}

== Overview ==
Wiki content here...

== History ==
More content...

{{CompanyEnd}}
</pre>

===Structure===
This template closes the following divs opened by <code><nowiki>{{Company}}</nowiki></code>:
* <code>.gb-company-wiki-content</code>
* <code>.gb-company-main</code>

Then renders the sidebar via <code><nowiki>{{CompanySidebar}}</nowiki></code> and closes:
* <code>.gb-company-content</code>
* <code>.gb-company-page</code>
</noinclude><includeonly>
</div>
<div id="DevelopedGames" class="gb-games-section" style="clear:both">
<div class="gb-games-section-header"><h2 class="gb-games-section-title">Developed Games</h2><span class="gb-view-all-btn">[{{fullurl:Special:Ask|q=%5B%5BHas+developers%3A%3A{{urlencode:{{FULLPAGENAME}}}}%5D%5D+%5B%5BCategory%3AGames%5D%5D&po=%3FHas+name%3DName%0A%3FHas+release+date%3DRelease&p=mainlabel%3D-2F&sort=Has+name&order=asc&limit=500&offset=0}} View all developed games]</span></div>
{{#invoke:CompanyGames|cards|developed|limit=12}}
</div>
<div id="PublishedGames" class="gb-games-section" style="clear:both">
<div class="gb-games-section-header"><h2 class="gb-games-section-title">Published Games</h2><span class="gb-view-all-btn">[{{fullurl:Special:Ask|q=%5B%5BHas+publishers%3A%3A{{urlencode:{{FULLPAGENAME}}}}%5D%5D+%5B%5BCategory%3AGames%5D%5D&po=%3FHas+name%3DName%0A%3FHas+release+date%3DRelease&p=mainlabel%3D-2F&sort=Has+name&order=asc&limit=500&offset=0}} View all published games]</span></div>
{{#invoke:CompanyGames|cards|published|limit=12}}
</div>
</div>
<div class="gb-company-sidebar">{{CompanySidebar}}</div>
</div>
</div>
</includeonly>
